{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01UYXFjXBseUiXL5jZCEfP7r","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The issue is clear. Pod `crdb-cluster-2` is running in TLS mode (`--certs-dir=/cockroach/cockroach-certs`) but pods 0 and 1 are still running in insecure mode (`--insecure`). The TLS handshake is failing because `crdb-cluster-2` is trying to connect to pods 0 and 1 over TLS, but they're still running insecure.\n\nThe rolling update didn't complete - it updated pod 2 (the highest number first, then works its way down) but the readiness probe is failing because it can't form a quorum with the other 2 nodes that are still in insecure mode. \n\nThis is the classic CockroachDB TLS migration problem - I can't do a rolling update because all nodes need to switch to TLS at the same time. The best solution is to delete all three pods simultaneously so they restart with the new TLS configuration together.\n\nSince the StatefulSet uses parallel pod management, I should force-delete all the pods at once. But first, let me check what revision each pod is currently running.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":6141,"cache_read_input_tokens":37206,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":6141},"output_tokens":18,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"7cfb7196-3a2d-4069-92d8-23c00446a073","uuid":"e7ffe041-1dcf-4b86-b544-a461fb6b049b","request_id":"req_011Ccfhd2N84zkwZKWevyW85"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01UYXFjXBseUiXL5jZCEfP7r","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The problem is clear: pod 2 switched to TLS but pods 0 and 1 are still insecure, so TLS handshakes fail across the cluster. I need to delete all three pods simultaneously so they all restart in TLS mode at once (the StatefulSet's `podManagementPolicy: Parallel` helps here):"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":6141,"cache_read_input_tokens":37206,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":6141},"output_tokens":18,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"7cfb7196-3a2d-4069-92d8-23c00446a073","uuid":"72b3d5a6-ab36-4aaa-9403-268b21830fed","request_id":"req_011Ccfhd2N84zkwZKWevyW85"}
